Description: The rest on the flight into Egypt with the Virgin holding Christ with outstretched arms Etching
Curator's comments: After Cantarini's painting in the Louvre Museum (inv. 175). A late impression on a sheet of paper with wide margins. For an early impression, see U.3-59.
Bibliographic references: Massari 1997 / In 'Simone Cantarini detto il Pesarese', ed. Andrea Emiliani (19.I)
Acquisition name: Donated by: Sir Augustus Wollaston Franks
